"A.P.238/4/15/11:20": "Such a painful voice, I can't bear to listen to it."
"But please tell me in the end, just what happened in that facility, that day?"
"For me in the Death Squad, what mission was going to be assigned to me?"
"That wasn't it was it? If that were all you wouldn't go on a rampage."
"That's why you need to tell me, please Hadred!"
"What was going to happen to me?"
"Really, how far will you go to protect a secret? You really are an idiot Hadred."
